I went back to Goodwill Computer Works for round two and couldn't help leaving with two carts full of retro gaming treasures. From a suspiciously cheap Xbox to a mysterious gaming PC with some interesting specs, every purchase was a gamble. The best part? Finding out that some of our donated parts were already on the shelves before we even left the store!
